 and the opposing team can’t win the game.','A',NULL,'N/A','5.69','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('401641','Serra Angel','V15','Creature — Angel','M','{3}{W}{W}','5','4','4',NULL,'Flying, vigilance','#_Born with wings of light and a sword of faith, this heavenly incarnation embodies both fury and purity._#',NULL,'Rebecca Guay','14','5',NULL,'W',NULL,'N/A','1.67','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('401642','Tariel, Reckoner of Souls','V15','Legendary Creature — Angel','M','{4}{R}{W}{B}','7','4','7',NULL,'Flying, vigilance£{T}: Choose a creature card at random from target opponent''s graveyard. Put that card onto the battlefield under your control.','#_"After death you face paradise, damnation, or Tariel."£—Priest''s teaching_#',NULL,'Wayne Reynolds','15','5','£9/22/2011: The only target of this ability is the opponent.£9/22/2011: The creature card is chosen at random from among creature cards in the target opponent’s graveyard as the ability resolves. Players can respond to the ability knowing the targeted player, but they won’t know which creature card is about to enter the battlefield.','WRB (O)',NULL,'N/A','2.99','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'RWB',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);